    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road for plenty more adventures with you! It drives beautifully and looks great, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something dependable and fun. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the right fit for you!",
