    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. It boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes for improved lateral stability and steering feedback. While the finish shows honest character from spirited use, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A precision-engineered machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable performance. Minor cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 28500.0,
